{"ja301:0.1":"Jataka ","ja301:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja301:0.3":"Kalingavagga ","ja301:0.4":"1. Culakalingajataka ","ja301:1.1":"“Vivarathimasam dvaram, ","ja301:1.2":"Nagaram pavisantu arunarajassa; ","ja301:1.3":"Sihena susitthena, ","ja301:1.4":"Surakkhitam nandisenena”. ","ja301:2.1":"“Jayo kalinganamasayhasahinam, ","ja301:2.2":"Parajayo anayo assakanam; ","ja301:2.3":"Icceva te bhasitam brahmacari, ","ja301:2.4":"Na ujjubhuta vitatham bhananti”. ","ja301:3.1":"“Deva musavadamupativatta, ","ja301:3.2":"Saccam dhanam paramam tesu sakka; ","ja301:3.3":"Tam te musa bhasitam devaraja, ","ja301:3.4":"Kim va paticca maghava mahinda”. ","ja301:4.1":"“Nanu te sutam brahmana bhannamane, ","ja301:4.2":"Deva na issanti purisaparakkamassa; ","ja301:4.3":"Damo samadhi manaso abhejjo, ","ja301:4.4":"Abyaggata nikkamananca kale; ","ja301:4.5":"Dalhanca viriyam purisaparakkamo ca, ","ja301:4.6":"Teneva asi vijayo assakanan”ti. ","ja301:5.1":"Culakalingajatakam pathamam. "}